                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Heat scorches those who lay eyes on the nightmarchers. All creatures in a @Template[type:cone|distance:60] take @Damage[15d6[fire]] damage (@Check[type:reflex|dc:34|basic:true] save).</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Prone] creatures and the nightmarchers' kin are unaffected as long as they have not taken a hostile action against the nightmarchers.</p>\n<p>The nightmarchers can't use Blazing Admonition for [[/br 1d4 #Recharge Blazing Admonition]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>"
