                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The nightmarchers fling a hail of spears and stones, dealing @Damage[(5d6+9)[bludgeoning]] damage or @Damage[(5d6+9)[piercing]] damage to creatures in a @Template[type:burst|distance:10] within 20 feet (@Check[type:reflex|dc:31|basic:true] save).</p>\n<p>When the nightmarchers are reduced to 8 or fewer squares, this decreases to a @Template[type:burst|distance:5].</p>"
