                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> to <span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span></p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The troop attacks with spears, clubs, and leiomano against enemies within @Template[type:emanation|distance:5]{5 feet} (@Check[type:reflex|dc:33|basic:true] save) for their choice of bludgeoning, piercing, or slashing damage depending on the number of actions.</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> @Damage[(2d6+2)[bludgeoning]] damage, @Damage[(2d6+2)[piercing]] damage, or @Damage[(2d6+2)[slashing]] damage</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> @Damage[(4d6+12)[bludgeoning]] damage, @Damage[(4d6+12)[piercing]] damage, or @Damage[(4d6+12)[slashing]] damage</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span> @Damage[(6d6+12)[bludgeoning]] damage, @Damage[(6d6+12)[piercing]] damage, or @Damage[(6d6+12)[slashing]] damage</p>"
